# AXIS / CORPUS POSITION
#   `fluffware/modbus_proxy` declares a **direct** dependency on
#   `tokio-modbus` (gated behind the `modbus_test` feature for
#   the auxiliary `modbus_sender` + `modbus_receiver` bins, with
#   the main `modbus_proxy` bin also relying on it through the
