#       RTU server endpoints
#     • Typed `Request::ReadCoils(addr, qty)` /
#       `Request::ReadHoldingRegisters(addr, qty)` /
#       `Response::ReadCoils(coils)` /
#       `Response::ReadHoldingRegisters(regs)` typed
